{
  "texts": [
    "Challenges are instances of task types, and developers choose whether to participate in these challenges.",
    "In this respect, Wang et al. [708] collected a dataset from Topcoder.",
    "Their dataset involved 32565 challenges, 7620 developers, and 59230 submissions spanning from 2006 to 2016.",
    "The dataset focused on 100 developers with over 100 submissions, containing the evolution of the skills of each developer.",
    "After filtering out submissions with a final score of 0 (indicating unfinished submissions), there were 74 developers left in the dataset."
  ]
}